WingSkeleton v0.1
=================


Description
-----------
The WingSkeleton is a  tutorial is basic WingS application to be filled with life by you.
It is only required to edit the "WingSSkeleteonSession.java"-file and recompile/build war to implement new functionality.

Installation
------------
Before installation, you need a working servlet container (eg. http://jakarta.apache.org/tomcat).
Also you will need a working ANT tool (http://jakarta.apache.org/ant).


Build the war-file by typing "ant war" at the command line and execute this.

The resulting "war"-file will be placed to the directory "build/packages". Copy, link or move this file to your servlet container war application directory and restart your servlet container. Before restarting, you should remove all old traces of the Application

